{
  "id": 2769,
  "name": "Lightblossom Trinity",
  "description": "The Lightbloom has suffered a terrible defeat, but like the rutaani it imbues, it changes. These Lightblossomed rutaani fanatically propagate their vicious and invasive garden.",
  "sections": [
    {
      "title": "Overview",
      "body_text": "The trio of Lightbloom rutaani work in tandem to sow and nurture a Lightblossom garden. Meittik creates [Fertile Loam] that is then planted by Lekshi's [Lightsower Dash]. Kezkitt rapidly germinates the flora with [Lightblossom Beam] until they burst in a [Lightbloom Overgrowth].",
      "spell": null,
      "sections": [
        {
          "title": "Damage Dealers",
          "body_text": "$bullet; Lightblossoms gain an increasing amount of [Light-Gorged] unless the rays of [Lightblossom Beam] are blocked.\r\n$bullet; Damage taken is shared between the trio with [Thicket's Trinity].",
          "spell": null,
          "sections": null
        },
        {
          "title": "Healers",
          "body_text": "$bullet; [Lightbloom Overgrowth] inflicts higher damage based on applications of [Light-Gorged].\r\n$bullet; [Thornblade] causes random players to bleed for high damage.",
          "spell": null,
          "sections": null
        },
        {
          "title": "Healers",
          "body_text": "$bullet; [Lightbloom Overgrowth] inflicts higher damage based on applications of [Light-Gorged].\r\n$bullet; [Thornblade] causes random players to bleed for high damage.\r\n$bullet; [Bedrock Surge] inflicts periodic damage to all players.",
          "spell": null,
          "sections": null
        },
        {
          "title": "Tank",
          "body_text": "$bullet; [Bedrock Slam] creates patches of [Fertile Loam] near the location of the target.\r\n$bullet; Lightblossoms gain an increasing amount of [Light-Gorged] unless the rays of [Lightblossom Beam] are blocked.",
          "spell": null,
          "sections": null
        }
      ]
    },
